<plot>PeaceJam helps today's youth confront the problems of hate and violence by engaging in a dialogue of peace. These young peacemakers are aided in their efforts by various Nobel Peace Prize Laureates who teach and help to put into practice the principles and actions of peace. PeaceJam: The Documentary follows the lives of five teens who have been changed due to their participation with PeaceJam.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?427090</url></doc>
